      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing M Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis integrity is excellent, with documented rear subframe reinforcement and a recent VANOS system overhaul to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The suspension remains tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings, providing precise turn-in and minimal body roll. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with its mileage, the powertrain delivers peak linear power and a visceral acoustic profile. This is a driver-focused machine with all major mechanical vulnerabilities addressed.",
